{"title":{"en":"B. Longest Common Substring","ru":"B. Наибольшая общая подстрока"},"contestId":"269656","problemIndex":"B","timeLimit":{"en":"2 seconds","ru":"2 секунды"},"memLimit":{"en":"512 megabytes","ru":"512 мегабайт"},"inputFormat":{"en":"standard input","ru":"стандартный ввод"},"outputFormat":{"en":"standard output","ru":"стандартный вывод"},"problemHtml":{"en":"<p>Find the longest common substring of two given strings $$$s$$$ and $$$t$$$.</p>","ru":"<p>Найдите наибольшую общую подстроку строк $$$s$$$ и $$$t$$$.</p>"},"inSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Input</div><p>First line of the input has single string $$$s$$$, second&nbsp;— $$$t$$$ ($$$1 \\le |s|, |t| \\le 100\\,000$$$). Strings are made of small latin letters.</p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Входные данные</div><p>Первая строка входного файла содержит строку $$$s$$$, вторая&nbsp;— $$$t$$$ ($$$1 \\le |s|, |t| \\le 100\\,000$$$). Строки состоят из строчных латинских букв.</p>"},"outSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Output</div><p>Output single line&nbsp;— the longest common substring of strings $$$s$$$ and $$$t$$$. Output lexicographically minimal one, in case of multiple possible answers.</p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Выходные данные</div><p>Выведите одну строку&nbsp;— наибольшую общую подстроку строк $$$s$$$ и $$$t$$$. В случае, если ответ не единственный, выведите минимальный лексикографически.</p>"},"noteHtml":{"en":null,"ru":null},"sampleTestcases":[{"id":1642262319614,"input":"bababb\nzabacabba\n","output":"aba\n","result":{"id":1642262319614,"stdout":"aba\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642262319615,"input":"qrdq\nrqqqrdqrqd\n","output":"qrdq\n","result":{"id":1642262319615,"stdout":"qrdq\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642262319616,"input":"hhhhhh\nhhhhhhh\n","output":"hhhhhh\n","result":{"id":1642262319616,"stdout":"hhhhhh\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642262319617,"input":"opopo\nppppopopo\n","output":"opopo\n","result":{"id":1642262319617,"stdout":"opopo\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}}],"submitUrl":"https://codeforces.com/edu/course/2/lesson/2/5/practice/contest/269656/submit","language":"c++","langId":"54"}